        "descriptions": [
          {
            "description": [
              {
                "text": "Peter, Linda, and Todd work as managers at Capital City Bank, a retail bank. Linda’s creative idea for attracting new customers to the bank has generated lots of new business."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Peter: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Great news! We had a "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"record-breaking"
            },
            {
              "text":	" quarter. We brought in revenues of $500,000."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Linda: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Wow, revenues really were "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"through the roof"
            },
            {
              "text":	"!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Todd: "
            },
            {
              "text": "That’s great. "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"Kudos to"
            },
            {
              "text":	" Linda! She deserves "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"a pat on the back"
            },
            {
              "text":	". The "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"guerrilla marketing"
            },
            {
              "text":	" campaign she "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"dreamed up"
            },
            {
              "text":	" was brilliant. She sent out e-mail to all of our customers asking them to e-mail a friend about our services. For each friend they e-mailed, they received a free gift."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Peter: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Linda, your campaign helped us "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"drum up a lot of business"
            },
            {
              "text":	". We "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"signed on 800 new customers"
            },
            {
              "text":	"."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Linda: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I’m really glad my plan "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"panned out"
            },
            {
              "text":	". I thought it would, since everybody loves a "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	" freebie"
            },
            {
              "text":	"!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Todd: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Linda, we can always count on you to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"think outside the box"
            },
            {
              "text":	"."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Linda: "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "For the record"
            },
            {
              "text":	", Peter helped me come up with the idea."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Peter: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Thanks for "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"sharing the credit"
            },
            {
              "text":	", Linda. But it was your idea."
            }
          ]
        }
        ,
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Todd: "
            },
            {
              "text": "The important thing is that we’re now "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"giving our"
            },
            {
              "text":	" biggest competitor, U.S. Bank, a "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"run for their money"
            },
            {
              "text":	"."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
